{"tid":585784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【兩會】青海省委書記：習近平總書記是活菩薩","createTime":"2018-03-09T03:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T06:56:18.000Z","uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a0f0ff0571dd08e6d6ec513a7d908aef12c10d41","tid":585784,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:30:09.000Z","msg":"中共青海省委書記王國生3月8日表示，住在青海省的藏人把習近平看做是神，視其為活菩薩。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報道，全國人大代表、青海省委書記王國生昨天在第13屆全國人民代表大會場邊表示，住在青海省的藏人曾說，他們把習近平看做是神。諷刺的是，青海省是流亡西藏精神領袖達賴喇嘛的出生地。<br />\n<br />\n王國生透露，青海省奉行中國已故領導人毛澤東啟發群眾熱愛黨、熱愛領袖的訓示。他說：「<strong>在牧區的老百姓說，習總書記才是活菩薩，這話說得很生動</strong>。」<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180309&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=57922624\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180309%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D57922624&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pvwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=b1eac309\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180309%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D57922624&h=4d74b96b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180309&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=57922624</a>"},{"pid":"4d2bc9a91e9bcbe2a07c938057adae0a478fb3e2","tid":585784,"uid":20241,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:44:25.000Z","msg":"老納學下人地啦<br />\n隨口up都精彩過你度左成朝份稿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe051a8291c1a9292e00590a72d3200040d9efd3","tid":585784,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:45:48.000Z","msg":"幾時全國性為習總建生祠？封9千歲？"},{"pid":"c49bb1226ac6873954af2da7b9d8d141bdd45c6f","tid":585784,"uid":75823,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fe051a8291c1a9292e00590a72d3200040d9efd3","tid":585784,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:45:48.000Z","msg":"幾時全國性為習總建生祠？封9千歲？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:47:00.000Z","